\title{on \em{[[eddison-the-worm-ouroboros]]}}
\author{ericczhao}
\date{2024-04-01}

\tag{thoughts}
\tag{books}

\p{The language is delightful, but one can't help but agree with [Tolkien](jrrtolkien)'s assessment ([Letter 199](tolkien-1981)) that what underlies the entire saga is "an evil and indeed silly 'philosophy'" and the ending has one wondering indeed if [Eddison](ereddison) admired "arrogance and cruelty."}
